      <div id="content">
	
<p>I am a post-doc in the <a href="https://team.inria.fr/parsifal/">Parsifal</a> team of Inria
Paris-Saclay and LIX, École Polytechnique, collaborating with Gabriel Scherer.</p>

<p>I work on the semantics of proofs and programs, and more specifically using
tools and point of view coming from linear logic, (higher) category theory,
realizability and intersection types.</p>

<p>I am also interested in bringing techniques from semantics not only to
verification, but also other aspects of computer science: making programming
more fun, or understable.</p>

<h3 id="contact-information">Contact information</h3>
<ul>
  <li>luc.pellissier@inria.fr</li>
  <li>Bâtiment Alan Turing<br>
Campus de Palaiseau</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="resum">Resumé</h3>
<p>In excruciating details in <a href="CV.pdf">French</a> and with much less details
in <a href="resume.pdf">English</a>.</p>

<h3 id="smiomaths">Sémiomaths</h3>

<p>I co-organize the <a href="semiomaths/">Sémiomaths</a> seminar. Feel free to drop by or
write us an e-mail!</p>

<h3 id="previous-positions">Previous positions</h3>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>During 2019, I was a post-doc in the pôle <a href="https://www.irif.fr/poles/pps/index">Preuves Programmes et
Systèmes</a> of the
<a href="https://www.irif.fr/">IRIF</a>, financed by the ANR project
<a href="https://www.irif.fr/~saurin/RAPIDO/">Rapido</a>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>During the austral 2018 academic year, I was a post-doc
<a href="http://www.pedeciba.edu.uy/indice.php">Pedeciba</a> at the <a href="http://el.pages.fing.edu.uy/website/en/index/">Logic
Group</a> of
<a href="https://www.fing.edu.uy/imerl">IMERL</a>, Universidad de la República, in
Montevideo, Uruguay. Legend has that I was the first uruguayan post-doc.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>In the fall 2017, I was an ATER (<em>attaché temporaire d'enseignement et de
recherche</em>, a temporary research and teaching position) at the <a href="http://www.ens-lyon.fr/DI">computer
science department</a> of <a href="http://ens-lyon.fr">ENS
Lyon</a> interacting with the <a href="http://www.ens-lyon.fr/LIP/PLUME/">plume
team</a>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Before that, from 2014-2017, I was a member of the <a href="https://lipn.univ-paris13.fr/fr/lcr-2" title="LoVe team">Lo♥Ve
team</a>, at the
<a href="http://lipn.univ-paris13.fr" title="LIPN">LIPN</a>, where I defended my
<a href="soutenance/">PhD</a>, prepared under the joint supervision of <a href="http://lipn.univ-paris13.fr/~mazza" title="Damiano Mazza">Damiano
Mazza</a> and <a href="http://lipn.univ-paris13.fr/~guerrini" title="Stefano Guerrini">Stefano
Guerrini</a>.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

